reviews.text: 普遍感覺良好，下午茶抵食，港式奶茶，水熱茶正｡
鮮牛蛋治+凍奶茶。兩款都有水平，值得推薦！
炒飯有雞蛋殼，唔係換左都重有少少，但服務幾好，唔會怪佢地，下次小心d就好啦！
出品不太穩定, 時好時壞, 勝在 晚餐有湯, 湯水不錯. 價錢合理

A big station with quite a lot of stores after entering the gate. There are toilets in the station but beware of the AB and CD exit are far away and make sure you know which way to go before you leave the station. There is a lift to the ground level near the Exit A.

Nice MTR station same as other MTR stations in Hong Kong. Nicely managed crowd system for peak hours. Very helpful staff. Quick access to exits. Easy and fast access using octopus cards. Good facility for wheel chair and strollers. Thanks to MTR staff and management for making the journey healthy and quick.
Easy interconnections to the linked stations

Good MTR station
